Class FoodItem<T extends FoodItem<T>>

java.lang.Object
FoodItem<T>
Type Parameters:
T - Generic types T for FoodItem
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Fruit, Preserve, Vegetable
public abstract class FoodItem<T extends FoodItem<T>> extends Object implements Comparable<T>
This abstract class represents a generic food item and provides methods to manage its properties.
Version:
2.0
